descript.abstract: stnetall displays all the streets in Pima County in a single-line representation.
descript.supplinf:
Known Errors/Qualifications: Urban streets from 12000 scale & rural streets from 100000 scale; 1/3 streets rectified to parcel base. Spatial Domain: Pima County Rectified: parcel Maintenance Organization: PC ITD GIS Maintenance Description: While this layer is maintained in the Enterprise Geodatabase, it is exported to shapefile maintenance format by a special process. Therefore, this layer's "Maintenance Format" reflects the format exported from the Geodatabase and not the true maintenance format.
The annotation is stored in the snetanno cover and should be updated there. Maintenance Frequency: Daily Maintenance Format: GDB Spec Export Primary Source Organization: PC DOT & DSD Primary Source Document: Orthophotos,Abandonments,Subdivisions,Parcel Split Primary Source Date: 1999 Primary Source Format: Shape Secondary Source Organization: USGS Secondary Source Document: Transportation DLG Secondary Source Date: 1988 Secondary Source Scale: 100000 GIS Contact: Ray Brice
MapGuide Layer Name: Streets - All MapGuide Scale Range: 0 - 50000
